item.title: About
item.description: About FANG META! FANG META! is created by FANG in Jan 18, 2022. It is mainly designed as heart tree cave serving for YOU and FANG to pour out heart respectively. Simultaneously, FANG META! serve as an atlas leading us toward a better future for humankind. About FANG FANG is now a junior undergraduate in an university sponsored by 985 Prdoject in Mainland China. Major in: Optoelectronic Information Science and Engineering
